If you want to create a new VM from the one time backup you have created, please follow the steps below:

- Login to client portal from https://portal.serverpoint.com/cgi-bin/gen4cp/engine/login.cgi
- Click "Deploy a new VM"
- choose the VM plan, size,location
- While selecting OS, click the drop down box below "choose one of your existing templates" and select the template OS.
